<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.9.5">
<l>pālaik kaṟantaṭup pēṟa vaittup</l>
<l rend="indent">palvaḷai yāḷeṉ makaḷi ruppa</l>
<l>mēlaiya kattē neruppu vēṇṭic</l>
<l rend="indent">ceṉṟiṟaip poḻutaṅkē pēci niṉṟēṉ</l>
<l>cāḷakki rāma muṭaiya nampi</l>
<l rend="indent">cāyttup parukiṭṭup pōntu niṉṟāṉ</l>
<l>ālaik karumpiṉ moḻiya ṉaiya</l>
<l rend="indent">yacōtai naṅkāyuṉ makaṉaik kūvāy.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>As my daughter, with many bangles,</l>
<l rend="indent">placed fresh milk upon the fire,</l>
<l>I went next door to ask for coal</l>
<l rend="indent">and stood there talking for for just a minute.</l>
<l>The prince of Śālagrāma [in the meantime]</l>
<l rend="indent">went around tipping over and drinking [the milk].</l>
<l>My lady, Yaśodā with sweet words like pressed sugar-cane,</l>
<l rend="indent">call your son!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
